RCA Cables A standard type of cable used to transmit analog audio and composite-video signals between devices such as televisions, satellite or cable receivers, VCRs, game console systems, speakers and more. Typical RCA cables will have two or three color coded connectors. RCA audio cables have two connectors: red (right stereo) and white or black for left stereo. An additional third connector on an RCA cable will be yellow for composite video. Splits a single RCA jack into 2 RCA outputs So you can easily connect up to 2 devices to a single source. Wide-Ranging Use For iPhone iPod iPad, MP3 Music player, Android smartphone tablet or PC desktop laptop with the common 3.5mm audio port And TV, AV receiver, amplifier, projector, radio, car audio, stereo system, Hi Fi audio, computer sound, recording equipment, speaker and more with 2RCA plug Features Connector A: 1 – 3.5(TRS) mm Mini-Jack (3 Position) Female Connector B: 1 – Stereo Audio (2 x RCA) Female, White (Audio left) Red (Audio right) Cable Length: 20cm Color: Grey Package Contents UGREEN 3.5mm Female to 2RCA Male Stereo Audio Cable Gold Plated x1

RCA Cables

A standard type of cable used to transmit analog audio signals between devices such as televisions, satellite or cable receivers, VCRs, game console systems, speakers and more. RCA audio cables have two connectors: red (right stereo) and white for left stereo.

Splits a single 3.5mm Female Jack into 2 RCA

UGREEN 3.5mm Female to 2 RCA Male Stereo Audio Y Cable Adapter is ideal for adapting the output of your PC or personal audio to stereo RCA jacks for a quick transition from headphone to rca connection.

Wide-Ranging Use

3.5mm Female Port, for iPhone iPod iPad, MP3 Music player, Android smartphone tablet or PC desktop laptop with the common 3.5mm audio port.

2RCA Connectors, for TV, AV receiver, amplifier, projector, radio, car audio, stereo system, Hi Fi audio, computer sound, recording equipment, speaker and more devices with 2RCA plugs.

Features

Connector A: 1 – 3.5(TRS) mm Mini-Jack (3 Position) Female

Connector B: 1 – Stereo Audio (2 x RCA) Female, White (Audio left) Red (Audio right)

Color: Grey

Package Contents

UGREEN 3.5mm Female to 2RCA Male Stereo Audio Cable Gold Plated x1
